    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you aren't a doctor but i'm just trying to figure out if there's even a known interaction or if it's just a general precaution. i read online that some antibiotics and statins can be tricky, but can you just tell me if clarithromycin specifically reacts with simvastatin? i'm just trying to decide if i should call my doctor tonight or if it's fine to just take them as usual.",
